CORE REQUIREMENTS
>> Create all sections of the mockup
>> Create multi-column layouts in the web page
>> Use an external CSS stylesheet to style your pages
>> Use either normalize.css or reset.css to reset your browser's default styles
>> Modify the box-sizing property of relevant elements to avoid nasty math
>> Follow naming conventions, maintain consistency across your .html and .css files
>> Indent nested elements to increase your code's readability

BONUS REQS
• Create and link to a second page, the Relaxr Blog.
  - The blog should have a two column layout
  - The left column should contain a few blog posts
  - The right column should contain a paragraph about Relaxr, an image of the Relaxr office, and a few links to Relaxr's partners (get creative)
